## Context

The kanban board needs real-time event push to all connected clients. The `ws@^8.16.0` library is already a production dependency in `server/package.json`. The `server/ws/` directory exists but is empty. The server uses an Express `createApp()` factory — WebSocket attachment happens by passing the HTTP server to `initWs()`. The client already has a Vite proxy rule for `/ws` with `ws: true`, confirming WebSocket support is expected.

